OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FThe UK's new defence secretary is
OL,7,Fmeeting with Nato counterparts at "a
OL,8,Fmoment of challenge" as he arrived in
OL,9,FBrussels without a defence investment
OL,10,Fplan.
OL,12,FDan Jarvis is meeting other defence
OL,13,Fministers at the Nato headquarters on
OL,14,FThursday, a day after the alliance's
OL,15,Fchief Mark Rutte said he expected all
OL,16,Fmember states to soon present "clear,
OL,17,Fconcrete and credible plans" for
OL,18,Fraising defence spending to 5% of
OL,19,Fgross domestic product (GDP) by 2035.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FBut Jarvis headed to Belgium without
OL,7,Fthe guarantee of extra funding to
OL,8,Fprepare the military for the growing
OL,9,Fthreats from hostile states like
OL,10,FRussia.
OL,12,FIt comes only three weeks before the
OL,13,FNato leaders' summit in Ankara, where
OL,14,Fspending plans are expected to be put
OL,15,Funder the spotlight by President
OL,16,FDonald Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FJarvis' predecessor, John Healey,
OL,7,Fresigned from the role last week over
OL,8,Fa row over planned funding in the DIP,
OL,9,Fclaiming that the plan was only going
OL,10,Fto provide an extra #13.5 billion,
OL,11,Ffalling short of the recommended #28
OL,12,Fbillion that defence officials had
OL,13,Fsaid was necessary.
OL,15,FBy 2035, Nato members are expected to
OL,16,Fcommit 3.5% GDP to core defence spend
OL,17,Fand a 1.5% GDP commitment to wider
OL,18,Fresilience spending.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FThe commitment Nato members are
OL,7,Fexpected to meet is split into a 3.5%
OL,8,FGDP core defence spending commitment
OL,9,Fand a 1.5% GDP commitment to wider
OL,10,Fresilience spending.
OL,12,FIn his resignation letter, Healey
OL,13,Fsuggested the UK was only committing a
OL,14,Fspend of 2.68% of GDP by 2030.
OL,16,FThe much-anticipated DIP remains
OL,17,Funpublished, but ministers insist it
OL,18,Fwill be released before the Nato
OL,19,Fleaders' summit on July 7.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the prime minister told
OL,7,FITV News that he "disagrees" with
OL,8,FHealey over the commitment to extra
OL,9,Fspending.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer said he had made
OL,12,Fclear to him that defence is and
OL,13,Falways would be "a focus, and a
OL,14,Fpriority".
OL,16,FIn brief remarks to the journalists
OL,17,Fupon his arrival at the Nato gathering
OL,18,Fon Thursday, Jarvis said it was "a
OL,19,Fhuge honour to be appointed by the
OL,20,Fprime minister last week".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FHe added: "It's very clear to me, as
OL,7,Fthe new defence secretary for the
OL,8,FUnited Kingdom, that this is a moment
OL,9,Fof challenge.
OL,11,F"The international security is
OL,12,Fincredibly challenging, and that's why
OL,13,Fthis gathering here today is so
OL,14,Fparticularly important."
OL,16,FJarvis said that Nato allies must
OL,17,Fcontinue supporting Ukraine's fight
OL,18,Fagainst Russia and bolster the
OL,19,Falliance's collective deterrence
OL,20,Fcapabilities, insisting the UK wants
OL,21,Fto work closely with European allies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
