PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Rutte issued a challenge
OL,12,Fto Nato members ahead of the July
OL,13,Fsummit, to "highlight how they're
OL,14,Fdelivering on commitments made in The
OL,15,FHague last year".
OL,17,FHe insisted that the 5% GDP investment
OL,18,Fwas "what we agreed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
