PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781794089
OL,3,CNew defence secretary heads to Nato
OL,4,Cmeeting without investment plan
OL,6,FSpeaking on Wednesday about this
OL,7,Fchallenge, defence minister Louise
OL,8,FSandher-Jones said Britain will show
OL,9,FNato its "strong commitment" to
OL,10,Fdefence by emphasising what it had
OL,11,Falready delivered, which she described
OL,12,Fas the "biggest increase in defence
OL,13,Fspending in a very long time".
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
